'''Eyes of Fire''' is a California-based [[sludge metal]] band formed in 1998 originally under the name Shiva.  In 2001 they signed with [[Century Media|Century Media Records]] and have since released one EP and two albums.

==Discography==
*''[[Disintegrate EP]]'' (2003)
*''[[Ashes to Embers]]'' (2004)
*''[[Prisons (Eyes of Fire album)|Prisons]]'' (2006)

